Package com.iontrading.mkv.bulkentitlements

Interface IMkvByFeatureReport

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<IMkvByFeatureUserReport>
    @Keep
@KeepPublicClassMemberNames
public interface IMkvByFeatureReport
extends Iterable<IMkvByFeatureUserReport>
    A wrapper object for the ByFeature Report.
    This object is related to specific Entitlement Namespace and can contain one or more reports on a per-user basis.
    Applications can browse the user-specific Reports contained in this object by simply iterating over the report or accessing a specific user Report by User Name.
    See Also:
    MkvEntitlementManager, MkvEntitlementManager.generateByFeatureReport(String, IMkvByFeatureEntitlementReportListener), MkvEntitlementManager.generateByFeatureReport(String, String, IMkvByFeatureEntitlementReportListener), MkvEntitlementManager.generateByFeatureReport(String, String, String, IMkvByFeatureEntitlementReportListener), IMkvByFeatureEntitlementReportListener, IMkvByFeatureReport, IMkvByFeatureUserReport, IMkvByFeatureReportRule, MkvByFeatureReportQuery
